01:29:39.379 --> 01:29:41.548
Ember, it's time.

01:29:46.720 --> 01:29:50.057
You know, I'm not really
one for tearful goodbyes.

01:29:50.807 --> 01:29:51.642
Wade.

01:29:52.309 --> 01:29:54.311
You big liar.

01:29:55.270 --> 01:29:57.439
Drip, drip, drip

01:29:57.606 --> 01:29:59.775
